## Title: WHO ATC/DDD Crawler and Parser
## Version: 0.2.0
## Date: 2026-07-14
## Author: Lucas VHH TRAN
## Maintainer: Lucas VHH TRAN <tranhungydhcm@gmail.com>

## Description:
## Comprehensive tools for crawling, parsing, and working with the WHO
## Anatomical Therapeutic Chemical (ATC) Classification System and Defined
## Daily Dose (DDD) Index. Provides robust HTTP retrieval with retries,
## rate limiting, and filesystem caching; parses hierarchical ATC codes and
## DDD specifications into tidy tables; offers offline drug name search,
## fuzzy matching, and DDD computation from prescription data.

